=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/EGauge.html#egauge\">egauge</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">U</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span>)</span></span>)</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.EventuallyLE\">≤ᶠ[</a><span class=\"fn\">l</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Filter/Defs.html#Filter.EventuallyLE\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">ε</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Convex/EGauge.html#egauge\">egauge</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">V</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">g</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span>)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Asymptotics/TVS.html#Asymptotics.IsLittleOTVS.exists_eventuallyLE_mul","kind":"theorem","line":94,"name":"Asymptotics.IsLittleOTVS.exists_eventuallyLE_mul","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Asymptotics/TVS.lean#L94-L94"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Asymptotics/TVS.html#Asymptotics.IsLittleOTVS.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Asymptotics</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsLittleOTVS</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\